{"tid":406141,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"到底應唔應該同manger吹水？","createTime":"2017-09-19T11:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T12:40:29.000Z","uid":127383,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1eb38f51af13bfaa412bc203e38d82a59877e7","tid":406141,"uid":127383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"入職半年，條team得9個人。除左個AM外冇乜人會buy個manager，講野成日懶好笑，人品聽講麻麻地，小氣兼記仇。<br />\n<br />\n近依個月manager有時會聊我吹水仲幾好傾，傾親都係低低能能大家一齊笑下，但其餘幾個從不參與吹水，佢地本身除左job上以外都少同manager交流。今日又吹下鄭中基d戲，你知幾多搞笑對白架啦，我份人本身又喜歡笑咪同manager吹多兩句囉，點知比人話我擦鞋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我冇諗過搏上位，我只係唔想得失任何人，依加比人話完好難受，我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千祈咪痴埋老細到啊，上位冇你份架喇，埋返同事堆算鳩數啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話撚知班同事啦，又唔係真心friend，繼續討老細歡心"},{"pid":"9b1b35765b6327fcee421cf45c94e7f96b2cec62","tid":406141,"uid":127383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"連登打救我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90545d4d3491e0ad281bc67a182e2fbc46b86517","tid":406141,"uid":52287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"你諗下邊個有權點你做野，就知應該討好邊個啦"},{"pid":"1c29dbd217c67456fed7f2315f0b213863a1155d","tid":406141,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"你估你同事無擦佢鞋咩<br />\n唔好做得太突出就ok"},{"pid":"45ef3b4a8b5f6a57a8bdf68b2398848b2a3ad14c","tid":406141,"uid":53798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"你做到野就無問題<br />\n<br />\n但有事唔好諗住manager 保你，可能佢當你傻仔咁玩，吹水only"},{"pid":"21fbcc867422421283d1e333c64030981bf14f1f","tid":406141,"uid":146495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09e1cb1c31