lockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n你諗太多"},{"pid":"68da44d8873b22874d971f55cf5803b1ed768aa6","tid":406141,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"你屋企有錢既話就唔洗理<br />\n你係窮撚既話就唔該你刷靚對鞋先啦<br />\n想成世俾人點?"},{"pid":"c3752474b8edc46ef2fb89f041a26932a451c2c3","tid":406141,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"擦鞋仔 幾時奶埋鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae799a3848ac00ea06a1b00b5da653207c8651b","tid":406141,"uid":127383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你屋企有錢既話就唔洗理<br />\n你係窮撚既話就唔該你刷靚對鞋先啦<br />\n想成世俾人點?</blockquote><br />\n做窮撚真係慘，依個世界公平咩"},{"pid":"f0dd1f1ddb987f56d176d0e4df2bbbe3efabc57a","tid":406141,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"講金唔講心基本啦"},{"pid":"e4362e59e449e7f01f6adea8c5322dbf608ce78b","tid":406141,"uid":127383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擦鞋仔 幾時奶埋鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇心擦鞋，只係咁啱話題啱key吹多兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}